    how_to_call: 'Call upon Ya Majid in moments of pure glorification — when you want to acknowledge Al-Majid\'s nobility independent of any personal need. Also call upon Him when your own dignity has been attacked or diminished — the connection to Al-Majid\'s nobility cannot be reached by any insult.',

