    meaning_deep: 'The One who advances and brings forward — who places things in their precise order and advances whom He wills in rank, in provision, in timing. Al-Muqaddim decides what comes first, who goes forward, what is given precedence. Every good thing that arrived in your life at the right time was Al-Muqaddim placing it there.',
