    quran_context: 'Al-Muqaddim and Al-Mu\'akhkhir together control the timing of all things. What He advances cannot be delayed. What He delays cannot be advanced. The timing of every good and every test is in His hands.',

    prophetic_usage: 'The Prophet ﷺ said: "Whatever Allah has decreed for a servant of provision, honor, or guidance — it will reach him, whether he seeks it diligently or with little effort." Al-Muqaddim advances what He has decreed. The advance is guaranteed by decree.',

    how_to_call: 'Call upon Ya Muqaddim when your progress feels blocked or stalled. When good things seem to be arriving too slowly. What Al-Muqaddim has decreed to advance will advance. Ask Him to advance what He has already written for you.',

