    reflection: 'The Prophet ﷺ called upon Al-Awwal and Al-Akhir together. The brackets of existence held him — before he began and after he would end. This is the security of the believer: you are held between Al-Awwal and Al-Akhir. Nothing can touch you outside those brackets. And those brackets are eternal.',
